card.name: CW - CCW256 - Link to the admins data for extracts

data.text:
@gillianoberholzer @cobuspienaar @neilbosworth @yasserogier 
Hi - Thanks to John and Sakkie, they found the missing code at least.
John provided me with the extract app on the old server.
It contains the admin order code which was omitted in the new app.

The problem wasn't on LAWCredit's side, but on ours.

Could someone who was dealing with this please confirm if the code was omitted for a reason or if it was an honest mistake?
